abel=\"Open menu\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"7\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"7\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"3\" y1=\"17\" x2=\"21\" y2=\"17\"></line></svg></button></div></nav></header><main><div style=\"background:var(--green-deep);padding:1rem 2rem 4rem;color:var(--cream)\"><div class=\"section-inner\"><div class=\"section-tag\" style=\"color:var(--gold);border-top-color:var(--gold)\">Get in Touch</div><h1 class=\"section-h2\" style=\"color:var(--cream);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)\">Contact <em style=\"color:var(--gold-light)\">the club</em></h1></div></div><div class=\"section-inner\" style=\"padding:4rem 2rem\"><div class=\"contact-grid\"><div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2.5rem\"><div><div class=\"section-tag\">Address</div><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Libre Baskerville&#x27;, serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text-mid)\">Sun Inn, Church Road<br/>Barnes, London<br/>SW13 9HE</p></div><div><div class=\"section-tag\">Email</div><a href=\"mailto:info@barnesbowling.com\" style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--green-mid)\">info@barnesbowling.com</a><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:6px;font-family:&#x27;Libre Baskerville&#x27;, serif;font-style:italic\">We aim to respond within 48 hours</p></div><div><div class=\"section-tag\">Season</div><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Libre Baskerville&#x27;, serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text-mid)\">25th April to early October<br/>Play 7 days a week 11am - 11pm weather permitting</p></div><div><div class=\"section-tag\">Social</div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;margin-top:.5rem\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/barnesbowlingclub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:13px;color:var(--green-mid);font-weight:500\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" style=\"width:18px;height:18px\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"2\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" rx=\"5\"></rect><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\"0.5\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke=\"none\"></circle></svg>Instagram</a><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/barnesbowlingclub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:13px;color:var(--green-mid);font-weight:500\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"width:18px;height:18px\"><path d=\"M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z\"></path></svg>Facebook</a></div></div></div></div><div style=\"background:var(--cream-warm);padding:2.5rem\"><a class=\"section-tag\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/apply\">Membership enquiry</a><h2 style=\"font-family:&#x27;Playfair Display&#x27;, serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:500;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:1rem\">Thinking of Joining?</h2><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:0.9rem\">If you&#x27;ve been wondering whether bowls might be for you, the best thing to do is come along and try. We&#x27;re a warm, welcoming Club and there&#x27;s nothing better than seeing the green for yourself.</p><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:0.9rem\"><strong>Wednesday Club Nights</strong>are the perfect introduction. From 6pm every Wednesday, it&#x27;s a relaxed, free social evening — no booking, no fee, no experience needed. Just turn up. You&#x27;ll meet Members and Committee Members, have a roll-up on the green, and get a real feel for the Club.</p><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:0.9rem\">There&#x27;s always someone happy to lend a hand and show you the ropes. Bowls is one of the few sports where women and men play together as equals — it&#x27;s social, surprisingly competitive when you want it to be, and good fun whatever the weather.</p><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:0.9rem\">A little about us — Barnes Bowling Club is home to <strong>London&#x27;s oldest bowling green</strong>, the original Elizabethan green where the game has been played since 1725. We have over <strong>100 Members</strong>, and we&#x27;re always delighted to welcome newcomers aged 18 and over.</p><p style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--green-deep);margin-bottom:2rem\"><strong>A note on formal applications:</strong> Before any application can be accepted, we ask that you have visited the Club and played with at least two Committee Members. Wednesday Club Nights are the easiest way to do this — and the best way for us to get to know each other.</p><a class=\"btn-gold\" style=\"display:inline-block;color:#ffffff\" href=\"/apply\">Submit a membership enquiry →</a></div></div></div></main><footer style=\"background:#f4f4f4\"><div style=\"max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 24px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:2.5rem;align-items:flex-start\"><div style=\"justify-self:start\"><a class=\"nav-brand\" style=\"margin-left:-2px;top:0\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"nav-brand-name\">BBC</span><span class=\"nav-brand-sub\">Est. <span class=\"nav-brand-sup\">c</span>1725</span></a></div><div><div style=\"font-family:&#x27;Optima&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-wei